channel.description:
[center][center][size=14pt][b]raputation Table[/b][/size][/center] Any posts in this thread, or pmd to me, will be reviewed and result in a change in this table. Please post in this thread/pm me if you wish to be added with the default rap of 10. raputation is in descending order from highest to lowest with the bounds of [-500, 500], with a few obvious exceptions. [code=java] Fat Cookies: 9001 Mopman: 12 Tom: 11 naseem142: 11 Pure_: 10 sk8rdude461: 10 Justin Bieber: 10 Eyeownyew: 10 Bowser jr: 10 Krackkid: 10 Sfacciato: 10 arham 4: 10 casey.: 9 The Enforcer: 9 tyb97: 8 nolan2131: 8 Lil_Smok3r: 6 lesterknome: 4 [/code] [center][size=14pt][b]rapping[/b][/size][/center] In order to rap somebody, a post must be made with proper formatting:
[i]username with ++ at end for adding rap, or -- for removing, linking to post that merits raputation.[/i]
Example:
[url=https://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,665417.msg4448130.html#new]lesterknome++[/url]
posted here, in this thread, would add one raputation to the user 'lesterknome', for the post linked. The amount of raputation you render to another user is found by your raputation, divided by 20, and truncated to the greatest interger. The bounds are [1, 25]. [center][size=14pt][b]Rules[/b][/size][/center] * You may rap each post by an individual user once. * You may rap any individual user once a day. * You may only make changes to others' raputation once every two hours. * You may not rap yourself. * Posts with improper formatting will not be processed in order to prevent abuse.
